VIRGINIA STATE INS. CO. v. A. B. FRANK & CO. GREENWICH INS. CO. v. SAME. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. January 5, 1904.) Nos. 1,226, 1,227. In Error to the Circuit Court of the United States for the Western District of Texas. N. W. Finley, for plaintiffs in error. Jno. Se-horn, for defendant in error.

Before PARDEE, McCORMICK, and SHELBY, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The judgments in both the above-entitled cases are affirmed.
